<body>
<div class="main_body">
    <h2 class="sa-section-title">About Us</h2>
    <p class="sa-section-subtitle">Get to know Winners Sports Academy</p>

    <div class="sa-about-section">
        <div class="sa-about-block animate-in">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Our Mission</h2>
            <p>At Winners Sports Academy, our mission is to provide top-notch training and development programs that empower athletes of all ages and skill levels. We aim to foster a passion for sports, promote a healthy lifestyle, and develop both physical and mental strength in our students.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="sa-about-block animate-in" style="animation-delay:0.1s">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-eye"></i> Our Vision</h2>
            <p>Our vision is to be a leading sports academy recognized for excellence in training, innovation in coaching techniques, and commitment to nurturing the next generation of athletes. We strive to create an environment where talent thrives and dreams are realized.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="sa-about-block animate-in" style="animation-delay:0.2s">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-clipboard-list"></i> Our Programs</h2>
            <p>We offer a wide range of programs including football, basketball, table-tennis, swimming, and more. Each program is designed to cater to the specific needs of our athletes, with a focus on skill development, teamwork, and sportsmanship. Our experienced coaches provide personalized training plans to help each athlete reach their full potential.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="sa-about-block animate-in" style="animation-delay:0.3s">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-building"></i> Our Facilities</h2>
            <p>Our state-of-the-art facilities include fully equipped gyms, indoor and outdoor courts, swimming pools, and training fields. We ensure that our athletes have access to the best resources and equipment to support their training and development.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="sa-about-block animate-in" style="animation-delay:0.4s">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-handshake"></i> Join Us</h2>
            <p>Whether you are a beginner looking to learn a new sport or an experienced athlete aiming to enhance your skills, Winners Sports Academy welcomes you. Join us and become part of a community that values dedication, excellence, and the love of sports.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="sa-about-block animate-in" style="animation-delay:0.5s">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-headset"></i> Reach Out</h2>
            <p><i class="fas fa-phone-alt" style="color:var(--accent-gold);margin-right:8px"></i> 8960136926</p>
            <p><i class="fas fa-envelope" style="color:var(--accent-gold);margin-right:8px"></i> vibhor1127@gmail.com</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

